videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Loyola Chicago's Braden Norris knocks down a 3-pointer from way downtown to give the Ramblers an early 7-0 lead over Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Norris fired up after hitting NBA-range 3 for Loyola Chicago) 2020/12/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Norris fired up after hitting NBA-range 3 for Loyola Chicago

videos.description: After falling behind 7-0 to Loyola Chicago early, Wisconsin rattles off four straight buckets to take the lead.
